{"tid":1638722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［投票］爆唔爆交通燈？ 交通督導員同交通警呢？","createTime":"2019-10-08T11:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T01:19:39.000Z","uid":20363,"like":16,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"350f8e19fbb0ad6afdffb4f7a300bb4280416591","tid":1638722,"uid":20363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"文宣：爆就爆左，屌政府點解無交通警同督導員啦，唔係俾左錢請人嘅咩？麻煩大家轉風向，推返個波俾政府，想好睇d就要人做義務交通員。<br />\n<br />\n爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n爆好處：<br />\n1，增加管治成本<br />\n2，幫人罷工或遲到<br />\n<br />\n爆壞處<br />\n1，失淺黃民意（無可否認）<br />\n2，無左黨鐵無埋其他運輸手段（繁忙時間）<br />\n3，睇唔到有罷工跡象，遲到居多"},{"pid":"4f3f3b25494bdccd0f00ed5c6e101a8bba09d4ed","tid":1638722,"uid":329466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:48:35.000Z","msg":"最尾個句唔認同 做咩撚野義工呀有時間番多份兼職課金喇屌"},{"pid":"c1b5cf6a1e671bd23930363f7f5ed53e16fcddc7","tid":1638722,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"今日見到交通警疏導交通，唸緊屌唔屌佢地好"},{"pid":"7a74892aeaa85f702c09efb6e25e703606ebfc80","tid":1638722,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:54:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"852fb4edfb8b621b34416fd7937c711253075696","tid":1638722,"uid":230658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"對慢動作老人家同殘疾人士極度唔方便，更會提高出意外機率。馬路如虎口，懇請各手足手下留情，或以癡貼紙暫時報廢交通功能?"},{"pid":"0f3a96c771a885e7d1c11958e95bedb4110a248f","tid":1638722,"uid":203190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"效益低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac4dff93697d2b0d70a3d061432be23e354714f","tid":1638722,"uid":130367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:31:49.000Z","msg":"1. 唔見有交通警，都係靠香港人自律先冇事，冇咩效果。<br />\n<br />\n2. 遲到居多，唔見有罷工跡象。<br />\n<br />\n結論：弊 &gt;&gt; 利，唔建議爆。"},{"pid":"485a5e91d4a08ed3ec3f56d4436a1e12b6fcec6d","tid":1638722,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:17:41.000Z","msg":"唔拆交通燈呀<br />\n黑裝修 紅裝飾 藍罷買 黃幫襯<br />\n跟規矩啦"},{"pid":"d9dcfee915675102d738bcd06747a128fcc2adb0","tid":1638722,"uid":65790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:18:41.000Z","msg":"唔爆，冇用同影響到自己人"},{"pid":"4246e8a006d7621f39007efd9565ecda0476e581","tid":1638722,"uid":20363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:19:20.000Z","msg":"其實已經證明左係黑警爆，推咩俾佢地"},{"pid":"66c4a1995900f56d24dd3668724cccb244f4f05f","tid":1638722,"uid":20363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4246e8a006d7621f39007efd9565ecda0476e581","tid":1638722,"uid":20363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:19:20.000Z","msg":"其實已經證明左係黑警爆，推咩俾佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:19:39.000Z","msg":"推哂"}]}